snippet.title: Judge Denies Amber Guyer Lawyers Request To Move Trial To Another County
snippet.description:
State District Judge Tammy Kemp, of the 204th Judicial District Court in Dallas, made her decision on an earlier motion from Guyger’s defense team asking that the trial be moved due to impartiality concerns regarding the jury

Hosted by Phillip Scott
